> `1cap` unit is not a valid CSS unit. The `cap` unit was proposed in a draft
> specification but it's not currently supported in any browser.
> 
> If you want to align the bottom edge of the button with the baseline of the
> text, you can use `vertical-align: middle;` or `vertical-align: text-bottom;`.
