> units like `em`, `px`, `%`, etc.
> 
> Here's an example:
> 
> ```html
> <button style="vertical-align: calc(1em - 3px);">button</button>
> ```
> 
> In this example, the `calc(1em - 3px)` expression calculates the vertical-align
> value by subtracting 3 pixels from 1em. The exact values will depend on your
> specific styles and might require some trial and error to get right.

